WEBVTT

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:42.760
Hey!

00:00:43.450 --> 00:00:44.600
I know you're in there.

00:00:44.950 --> 00:00:46.152
Are you going to open the door or not?

00:00:46.176 --> 00:00:47.176
If not…

00:00:52.576 --> 00:00:55.976
Ti… Tiger, please don't hurt me.

00:00:56.008 --> 00:00:57.384
My kid just started school.

00:00:57.408 --> 00:00:58.968
I can't come up with the money in time.

00:01:12.470 --> 00:01:13.112
You can't come up with the money,

00:01:13.128 --> 00:01:14.624
or you can't stop spinning the slots? Huh?

00:01:14.648 --> 00:01:15.900
I'm really sorry.

00:01:15.928 --> 00:01:17.192
Please don't hurt me.

00:01:17.224 --> 00:01:19.190
I'll do anything you want.

00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:21.856
I'm sorry. I really am.

00:01:21.888 --> 00:01:22.488
I'm sorry.

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:23.200
I'm sorry, bro.

00:01:23.232 --> 00:01:24.928
I'm really sorry. Please don't hurt me.

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:27.088
I'm sorry. I beg you.

00:01:27.980 --> 00:01:29.176
I'm sorry.

00:01:29.216 --> 00:01:30.216
Argh!

00:01:46.710 --> 00:01:47.992
If you don't pay me by tomorrow,

00:01:49.460 --> 00:01:51.200
you'll end up like this phone.

00:01:55.144 --> 00:01:56.144
Understood.

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:00.640
This is the last stop.

00:02:01.030 --> 00:02:02.440
Boss said this one's the toughest.

00:02:02.888 --> 00:02:03.816
I don't know why.

00:02:03.856 --> 00:02:05.728
Anyone who walks in here goes soft

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:07.240
and never comes back with the payoff.

00:02:07.660 --> 00:02:09.144
Well, well, well.

00:02:09.570 --> 00:02:11.640
They've got money to open a cat café,

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:13.016
but they can't pay off their debt.

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:14.280
What's wrong with them?

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:48.600
Hey, Dong.

00:02:49.690 --> 00:02:50.720
You can go back first.

00:02:50.752 --> 00:02:51.752
What?

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:55.680
I'll take care of this case.

00:03:06.570 --> 00:03:08.248
You can hold him.

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.072
Go ahead.

00:03:11.100 --> 00:03:12.216
You can hold any of my cats here.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.470
Just don't take them home.

00:03:19.060 --> 00:03:20.060
Well, I…

00:03:20.940 --> 00:03:22.272
I'm allergic to cat fur.

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:23.800
Oh, really?

00:03:26.370 --> 00:03:28.130
But you're okay just
looking at them, right?

00:03:31.130 --> 00:03:32.184
Jiro,

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:33.912
keep your distance.

00:03:33.936 --> 00:03:35.216
Social dis-cat-ing, dear.

00:03:36.580 --> 00:03:37.688
There he goes.

00:03:49.088 --> 00:03:50.088
Well…

00:03:50.270 --> 00:03:50.816
actually, I'm here for...

00:03:50.848 --> 00:03:52.820
Are you here for a cat fix?

00:03:56.460 --> 00:03:57.968
You must take off your shoes first.

00:03:58.540 --> 00:03:59.680
Welcome.

00:04:09.624 --> 00:04:12.400
Every cat here is a stray
that was abandoned.

00:04:12.424 --> 00:04:15.352
Cats are like people, you know?

00:04:15.368 --> 00:04:16.888
Even if they're the same breed,

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:18.440
they all have different personalities.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:21.248
(Most of them like being alone, though.)

00:04:25.250 --> 00:04:27.250
(Cats like things neat and orderly.)

00:04:31.870 --> 00:04:33.536
(Looking good is their top priority.)

00:04:50.500 --> 00:04:53.168
(People usually think
cats don't understand us, )

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:54.944
(but they actually understand
everything we say.)

00:04:54.968 --> 00:04:56.936
(It's totally up to them
whether they feel like responding.)

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:59.976
I feel truly honored to visit Thailand.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:03.784
I love the racetracks here,
Thai food, and Thai massages.

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:09.744
But what I love most is…

00:05:10.750 --> 00:05:12.136
the Thai smile.

00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:22.648
My work here is done.

00:05:22.672 --> 00:05:26.624
You can freely enjoy
the party, Mr. Enrique.

00:05:26.648 --> 00:05:27.984
Have fun.

00:05:32.380 --> 00:05:34.224
Aren't you coming with me?

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:37.328
I still want to talk to you.

00:05:37.384 --> 00:05:40.280
(When you talk to cats,
you need to listen with your eyes.)

00:05:40.312 --> 00:05:43.112
(They respond to us
through their body language.)

00:05:43.570 --> 00:05:46.304
(If cats get angry,
they flick their tails.)

00:05:46.328 --> 00:05:49.064
(You'd better run,
or they might scratch you.)

00:05:49.088 --> 00:05:50.888
Do you want to add a
cat to your friend list?

00:05:50.950 --> 00:05:52.120
Huh?

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.952
Make eye contact and blink slowly.

00:05:55.976 --> 00:05:58.576
If they blink back, it means
they've accepted your friend request.

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:05.488
Or if you want to go
somewhere else with me,

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:07.080
I'm fine with that too.

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:15.248
How about coming to my room?

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:20.152
My partner, who's an
F1 fan, is waiting for me.

00:06:20.176 --> 00:06:23.688
I'm sure you'll spend
the whole night talking together.

00:06:38.380 --> 00:06:40.232
Looks like his friend list is full.

00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:41.580
It's alright.

00:06:42.990 --> 00:06:44.256
I'll go find you a new boss.

00:06:46.100 --> 00:06:50.504
HOPE YOU FIND YOUR FAVORITE CAT.

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:53.456
I've got plenty of cat bosses for you
to choose from.

00:06:53.480 --> 00:06:54.480
Come here.

00:06:56.660 --> 00:06:58.376
Go ahead, make your pick.

00:06:58.900 --> 00:07:00.144
Which boss do you like?

00:07:00.168 --> 00:07:03.384
JUMBO, JIRO, JENNIE

00:07:11.072 --> 00:07:14.416
LYNX.

00:07:18.368 --> 00:07:20.370
That one is named Lynx. He's my son.

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:22.672
He ran off and became a stray.

00:07:22.712 --> 00:07:24.000
He's a tough nut to crack.

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.384
If anyone can make him blink back,

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:27.728
I'm ready to give him up,

00:07:27.768 --> 00:07:28.928
along with this café.

00:07:33.500 --> 00:07:37.224
LYNX.

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:43.700
"Cat for Cash" (Episode 1)

00:08:47.740 --> 00:08:50.784
Je Meow, your ice is here.

00:08:51.470 --> 00:08:52.408
Close the door for me, Krapor.

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.304
The cats might sneak out.

00:08:53.328 --> 00:08:54.112
Oops, I forgot.

00:08:54.136 --> 00:08:55.136
I knew it.

00:08:57.180 --> 00:08:59.856
This cold guy is yours.

00:08:59.910 --> 00:09:01.048
My whole arm's already numb.

00:09:01.940 --> 00:09:04.040
Then hurry up and fill it.

00:09:04.072 --> 00:09:04.512
So cold.

00:09:04.544 --> 00:09:06.510
Always with an intro.

00:09:07.570 --> 00:09:09.024
You're such a punctual guy.

00:09:09.048 --> 00:09:10.800
No wonder Jennie loves you so much.

00:09:12.150 --> 00:09:13.800
Sadhu.

00:09:14.220 --> 00:09:15.760
I've spent a fortune on her cat treats.

00:09:15.784 --> 00:09:17.568
Still, she won't even let me hold her paws.

00:09:17.608 --> 00:09:19.570
That's why that song was written,

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:22.664
♪ I shed my tears at a cat café ♪

00:09:23.136 --> 00:09:24.080
Don't give up just yet.

00:09:24.104 --> 00:09:24.752
Why, Sis?

00:09:24.768 --> 00:09:25.824
Just wait and see this man.

00:09:25.848 --> 00:09:26.848
Who?

00:09:27.700 --> 00:09:28.700
Here he is.

00:09:29.010 --> 00:09:30.000
5

