4

00:09:31.152 --> 00:09:32.208
3

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.240
2

00:09:38.390 --> 00:09:40.640
Welcome to Cat-Cheer Café.

00:09:42.300 --> 00:09:43.288
Jiro.

00:09:43.312 --> 00:09:43.976
Jiro, my boy.

00:09:44.008 --> 00:09:45.688
I've got to respect Tiger's dedication.

00:09:45.728 --> 00:09:48.064
He's been here, same time, same place,
every day for three months.

00:09:48.088 --> 00:09:50.608
Jiro still hasn't blinked back at him.

00:09:51.420 --> 00:09:53.848
At first, he was like a sugar cat daddy.

00:09:54.380 --> 00:09:54.896
Jiro.

00:09:54.920 --> 00:09:56.248
When treats didn't work,

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:58.048
he spoiled him with gadgets instead.

00:10:05.880 --> 00:10:07.632
But lately, he's been
coming in empty-handed.

00:10:07.656 --> 00:10:09.768
He's probably given up.

00:10:09.792 --> 00:10:11.088
Said who?

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:13.312
He's been wearing the same old shirt
for like a month.

00:10:13.336 --> 00:10:13.824
Huh?

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:18.288
He must've heard
cats recognize people by scent.

00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:21.608
Let's see if he finally gets recognized.

00:10:25.850 --> 00:10:26.850
Jiro.

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:31.840
Jiro.

00:10:32.500 --> 00:10:33.624
Let's be friends.

00:10:43.380 --> 00:10:44.380
Yes!

00:10:45.180 --> 00:10:46.766
Jiro finally accepted his friend request.

00:10:46.790 --> 00:10:47.790
Let's go over there.

00:10:49.460 --> 00:10:50.120
Yes!

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:52.240
That was amazing, Tiger.

00:10:52.304 --> 00:10:54.696
Jiro finally accepted your friend request.

00:10:55.048 --> 00:10:56.048
Hey, Je Meow.

00:10:58.360 --> 00:10:59.608
This isn't Jiro.

00:11:02.260 --> 00:11:03.260
Huh?

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:05.744
They look really similar,

00:11:06.540 --> 00:11:08.144
but Jiro has bigger eyes

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:09.760
and chubbier cheeks.

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:13.624
Come on, no drama.

00:11:13.648 --> 00:11:15.200
I'm just messing with you.

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.096
You're good, though.

00:11:16.128 --> 00:11:17.248
You remembered Jiro.

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:19.608
This is another orange cat
someone's letting me look after for now.

00:11:19.632 --> 00:11:21.304
So I rotated him in with Jiro.

00:11:25.640 --> 00:11:26.168
Here you go.

00:11:26.192 --> 00:11:27.632
There he is.

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:30.024
Your Jiro.

00:11:30.048 --> 00:11:30.824
Jiro.

00:11:31.024 --> 00:11:33.020
Tiger's here.

00:11:33.056 --> 00:11:34.280
Tiger could remember you.

00:11:34.312 --> 00:11:35.552
Give him a reward.

00:11:46.810 --> 00:11:49.984
This is the real Jiro,
with the verified blue checkmark.

00:11:50.008 --> 00:11:51.216
Congrats.

00:11:52.740 --> 00:11:53.740
Je Meow.

00:11:54.860 --> 00:11:57.000
Can I take a picture of Jiro
for my phone wallpaper?

00:11:57.032 --> 00:11:58.032
Sure. Go ahead.

00:11:58.240 --> 00:11:59.968
How about I take it for you?

00:12:05.970 --> 00:12:07.480
Make sure Jiro looks handsome.

00:12:08.968 --> 00:12:10.312
Nice.

00:12:15.690 --> 00:12:18.832
(Our condo doesn't allow cats,
in case someone here didn't know.)

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:23.216
What's up?

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:26.976
(Hey, Lynx. We're all here.
(Where the hell are you?)

00:12:28.580 --> 00:12:29.944
On my way.

00:12:29.984 --> 00:12:33.640
(Be real. Aren't you still at home
and standing us up?)

00:12:33.990 --> 00:12:36.024
Good. If you already know, I'm hanging up.

00:12:36.048 --> 00:12:40.552
(Hold on. Remember telling me
you were looking for a full-time job?)

00:12:40.608 --> 00:12:44.416
(One of my clients is looking for
a full-time interpreter in Melbourne.)

00:12:45.300 --> 00:12:48.272
(It's tough work, but the pay's huge.)

00:12:48.312 --> 00:12:49.304
When does it start?

00:12:49.328 --> 00:12:50.424
(Next month.)

00:12:51.250 --> 00:12:53.688
(It's a long-term contract, though.)

00:12:54.300 --> 00:12:57.088
(If I could stand being away from my bae,
I'd go myself.)

00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:23.960
Tiger!

00:13:25.460 --> 00:13:26.600
Hi, Je Meow.

00:13:27.130 --> 00:13:28.376
Those are for Jiro?

00:13:28.408 --> 00:13:29.408
Yes.

00:13:30.200 --> 00:13:32.904
I'm not sure which one he'll like.

00:13:34.390 --> 00:13:35.824
Pick the blue one.

00:13:35.856 --> 00:13:37.528
Jiro told me he likes blue.

00:13:40.010 --> 00:13:41.520
You can talk to cats?

00:13:41.750 --> 00:13:42.750
Shhh.

00:13:45.380 --> 00:13:47.688
Yes, I can talk to cats.

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:53.270
Kidding.

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:58.368
Cats see blue better than red.

00:13:58.620 --> 00:13:59.620
Oh.

00:14:00.140 --> 00:14:01.140
It's in their nature.

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:02.960
I see.

00:14:06.540 --> 00:14:07.832
He's gonna like it.

00:14:09.960 --> 00:14:10.960
After you.

00:14:12.512 --> 00:14:14.510
Thanks for helping me carry these bags.

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:18.848
Why did you buy so much stuff?

00:14:19.630 --> 00:14:23.120
I bought ingredients
to make fried noodles for Lynx.

00:14:23.144 --> 00:14:24.488
It's his favorite.

00:14:24.520 --> 00:14:25.976
He's dropping by.

00:14:26.500 --> 00:14:28.184
I bought enough to make extra for you too.

00:14:29.580 --> 00:14:31.968
I saw you always checking out
Lynx's pictures.

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:34.640
No, I didn't.

00:14:34.680 --> 00:14:37.520
Come on, I'm kidding.

00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:41.456
I actually wanted to cook for you

00:14:41.496 --> 00:14:44.104
to thank you for going easy on me
about the debt.

00:14:44.750 --> 00:14:45.750
So…

00:14:47.260 --> 00:14:50.232
you already knew who I was?

00:14:50.580 --> 00:14:51.656
I did.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:55.360
I'm sorry for paying back late.

00:14:55.392 --> 00:14:57.952
I haven't been well,
so I had to close the café a lot.

00:14:58.290 --> 00:14:59.290
But I promise

00:14:59.620 --> 00:15:01.304
I'll pay off the debt as soon as I can.

00:15:02.130 --> 00:15:03.130
Okay.

00:15:04.060 --> 00:15:06.728
Why didn't you ask Lynx to help you out?

00:15:07.050 --> 00:15:12.328
Oi, I was already glad
he even picked up my calls.

00:15:12.368 --> 00:15:14.330
We haven't talked in three years.

00:15:15.256 --> 00:15:17.260
I don't know if something's going on.

00:15:20.970 --> 00:15:22.130
My son's a tough case, right?

00:15:22.570 --> 00:15:24.024
Want to give it a shot?

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:26.432
If you win him over,
the cat café's included.

00:15:26.456 --> 00:15:27.456
I'll give it to you.

00:15:31.100 --> 00:15:32.264
You're interested, right?

00:15:33.030 --> 00:15:34.030
Let's go.

00:15:41.400 --> 00:15:42.400
Oi.

00:15:45.900 --> 00:15:46.900
Are you alright?

00:15:49.416 --> 00:15:50.416
You okay?

00:15:53.380 --> 00:15:54.624
I'm okay.

00:15:56.380 --> 00:15:57.360
I'll be fine.

00:15:57.392 --> 00:15:58.792
Just something that comes with age.

00:16:03.400 --> 00:16:04.096
Let's go.

00:16:04.144 --> 00:16:05.144
I'm okay now.

00:16:05.560 --> 00:16:06.640
Let's go eat fried noodles.

00:16:17.380 --> 00:16:18.380
Oh!

00:16:19.140 --> 00:16:20.480
What time is it already?

00:16:21.380 --> 00:16:24.000
Gosh, Lynx still isn't here?

00:16:25.520 --> 00:16:27.968
Should you call him?

00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:33.336
He probably had something urgent.

00:16:33.710 --> 00:16:34.710
It's fine.

00:16:38.323 --> 00:16:42.729
No matter how urgent, he could've called.

00:16:46.580 --> 00:16:47.736
It's alright.

00:16:48.900 --> 00:16:52.184
Just knowing he'd come
already makes me happy.

00:16:53.820 --> 00:16:58.584
I even thought he'd never
step foot in here again.

00:17:00.750 --> 00:17:04.720
Cat owners get used
to being ignored by cats.

00:17:05.940 --> 00:17:07.496
But when it's your own kid,

00:17:08.430 --> 00:17:10.536
no matter how long it's been,

00:17:12.540 --> 00:17:13.960
you never get used to it.

00:17:19.930 --> 00:17:21.976
It's pretty late now, Tiger.

00:17:23.050 --> 00:17:24.128
You should head home.

00:17:24.990 --> 00:17:27.784
I'll pack you my Korat fried noodles.

00:17:28.390 --> 00:17:29.192
You'll love it.

00:17:29.224 --> 00:17:30.312
You don't have to.

00:17:30.344 --> 00:17:32.856
Come on, my cooking's really good.

00:17:32.880 --> 00:17:33.832
I don't want to trouble you.

00:17:33.848 --> 00:17:35.224
Try them.

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:09.416
Je!

00:18:09.624 --> 00:18:10.624
Je Meow!

00:18:12.712 --> 00:18:14.816
Je, Je Meow.

00:18:16.530 --> 00:18:17.530
Je!

00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:18.600
Je!

00:18:23.470 --> 00:18:25.992
Meow~

