(Hey! Call an ambulance now!)

00:18:42.310 --> 00:18:43.048
(What do we do?)

00:18:43.096 --> 00:18:44.016
(What happened?)

00:18:44.048 --> 00:18:45.376
(What's wrong?)

00:18:45.408 --> 00:18:46.528
(What's wrong with Je Meow?)

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:52.760
(Why is Je Meow on the floor?)

00:18:53.480 --> 00:18:55.016
(Have you called an ambulance?)

00:18:55.456 --> 00:18:57.040
(Call an ambulance. Call it now.)

