Hello, someone passed out.

00:19:02.540 --> 00:19:03.992
Please send an ambulance right away.

00:19:04.580 --> 00:19:07.624
PUNARI VILAWONG
8 AUGUST 1980 - 23 MARCH 2025

00:19:28.850 --> 00:19:30.296
Where the hell were you that night?

00:19:31.660 --> 00:19:33.024
Do you know your mother…

00:19:33.730 --> 00:19:35.210
waited for you until her last breath?

00:19:59.500 --> 00:20:00.144
Hey!

00:20:00.460 --> 00:20:01.460
Hey!

00:20:02.780 --> 00:20:03.780
Hey!

00:20:03.880 --> 00:20:04.880
Hey!

00:20:15.370 --> 00:20:16.744
I asked around.

00:20:17.510 --> 00:20:19.656
It doesn't seem like anyone knows much.

00:20:20.350 --> 00:20:23.184
They said his father
died when he was little.

00:20:23.570 --> 00:20:25.056
They cut ties with their family.

00:20:25.830 --> 00:20:27.976
His mother got pregnant
before the marriage.

00:20:28.001 --> 00:20:29.761
So he's been handling
everything on his own.

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:44.680
Here.

00:20:54.640 --> 00:20:55.640
Do you feel better now?

00:20:58.760 --> 00:20:59.784
Who are you?

00:21:02.020 --> 00:21:03.184
My name is Tiger.

00:21:05.180 --> 00:21:06.696
I took your mother to the hospital.

00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:13.032
Oh, it was you. Thank you.

00:21:15.650 --> 00:21:16.650
So…

00:21:19.470 --> 00:21:20.608
what happened that night?

00:21:25.750 --> 00:21:26.552
Something came up.

00:21:26.577 --> 00:21:27.577
What was it?

00:21:38.064 --> 00:21:39.064
I'm sorry.

00:21:45.030 --> 00:21:46.456
You should eat.

00:21:54.730 --> 00:21:55.730
