00:22:56.430 --> 00:22:58.544
And it's been overdue for several months.

00:23:04.820 --> 00:23:06.328
Legally speaking,

00:23:06.633 --> 00:23:08.281
parents' debts…

00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:10.504
don't pass on to the child, right?

00:23:10.984 --> 00:23:12.980
Now that's the plot twist.

00:23:13.040 --> 00:23:14.592
But legally,

00:23:15.740 --> 00:23:18.560
