will be used to pay the debt.

00:23:19.490 --> 00:23:20.720
So you have to choose.

00:23:21.300 --> 00:23:22.152
Keep running this café,

00:23:22.184 --> 00:23:23.664
or go find the money and pay me back.

00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:26.464
Otherwise, I take the place.

00:23:28.576 --> 00:23:30.176
(Yeah, we're definitely losing the café.)

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:32.336
(There's no way Lynx wants
to keep this place going.)

00:23:32.368 --> 00:23:35.992
(But it's the only thing
Je Meow left for him.)

