00:24:50.070 --> 00:24:51.240
What's going on, Lynx?

00:24:51.272 --> 00:24:52.272
Lynx.

00:24:52.360 --> 00:24:53.232
What happened?

00:24:53.264 --> 00:24:55.424
Jiggo ripped my graduation gown.

00:24:56.430 --> 00:25:00.288
