00:26:48.800 --> 00:26:50.624
Have you decided

00:26:51.900 --> 00:26:53.192
what to do with the café?

00:26:56.740 --> 00:26:58.136
I'm not going to continue it.

00:26:59.228 --> 00:27:00.520
