00:27:00.544 --> 00:27:03.144
(See? I knew it.)

00:27:03.176 --> 00:27:05.488
(Then where are we supposed to be now?)

00:27:07.090 --> 00:27:08.090
And…

00:27:08.690 --> 00:27:10.320
