00:27:11.720 --> 00:27:12.784
Well…

00:27:13.790 --> 00:27:16.880
I'll find people to adopt them, I guess.

00:27:18.512 --> 00:27:19.784
Or I'll send them to a foundation.

00:27:19.808 --> 00:27:22.488
(Granny Joo, what is a "foundation"?)

00:27:22.528 --> 00:27:26.824
(It's where they separate us
and send us to different places.)

00:27:26.848 --> 00:27:28.712
(What? No way.)

00:27:28.736 --> 00:27:32.400
